    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and wear on the driver's seat, though all major electronics and the air conditioning are still functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that has been maintained regularly but shows the expected wear of its years.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows signs of regular use over the years. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's side bolster, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future to meet safety standards. It is a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work, but it is no longer in showroom condition.",
      "price": 20000.0,
